snippet.title: Wild West Dynasty - Official Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
Explore the world of Wild West Dynasty, a unique mix of RPG, life simulation and town building. This making of featurette gives you a taste of what it'll be like to conquer the Wild West, creating your own Dynasty which will last for decades.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
